BOMBERMAN: to run the code you need to run the file game.py in python 3. i.e. the command "python3 game.py" will start the game.
controls:
'q'-quit game
'w'-move up
's'-move down
'a'-move left
'd'-move right
'b'-plant the bomb at current position which will explode after 3 frames(any button pressed is considered as a frame) and the explosion lasts for 1 frame.
no. of lives - 3
 